column5: I don't know if this has been posted before but have a look if you like.http://www.cbc.ca/natureofthings/episodes/carpe-diem-a-fishy-story .
I saw most of it, they better fill in that canal. The electric harried won't stop them. Eggs will get through.
They made it  sound like it's inevitable that they'll get into the Great Lakes and beyond
